channel.title: Cache Help?
channel.description:
I was wondering how come when I add the cache files into the client folder to compile it and stuff, When I do compile it says it has compiled, but when I run the client the stuff I changed hasnt been changed to the new version of it.
Example: I changed the look of admin crown, I compile and it's still the same crown
